feature: Brand new boxes. Limited edition. Has rubber tires. Detailed exteriors. Officially licensed product. Die cast metal body and chassis. Each model is packed in individual blister pack. Dimensions of each car is approximately L-2 1/2 inches long. Might come with a chase car instead of one of the cars in a set.

Includes: 1976 Ford Mustang II Cobra II - Charlie's Angels (1976–81 TV Series) ; 1983 GMC Vandura - The A-Team (1983-87 TV Series); 1977 Dodge Monaco Metropolitan Police - The Terminator (1984); 1968 Shelby GT500KR Convertible - Gas Monkey Garage (2012-Current TV Series); 2011 Dodge Charger SXT - John Wick (2014); 2008 Ford Crown Victoria Taxi - John Wick: Chapter 2 (2017)
